<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-logo">
      <%= image_tag @logo %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">Withdrawal Request</h2>
    <p>
      You've requested to withdraw <%= @record.amount %> <%= @record.currency %>
      <br>
      to this address: <%= @record.rid %>
      <br>
      <br>
      Before going further with the withdrawal, please <strong>check carefully the target address.</strong> Be aware that if you confirm an incorrect address, we won't be able to assist you to recover your assets.
      <br>
      Verification code:
      <br>
      <br>
      <span class="confirm_code"><%= @record.code %></span> or <a clicktracking=off target="_blank" href="<%= @record.domain %>/confirmation/withdrawal?tid=<%= @record.tid %>&confirmation_code=<%= @record.code %>&action=confirm">click here</a> to confirm your withdrawal
      <br>
      <br>
      The verification code will be valid for 30 minutes. Please do not share this code with anyone.
      <br>
      If you do not receive this activity, please immediately disable your account, contact us at <a target="_blank" href="#">https://www.zsmart.tech/vn/support</a> and <a clicktracking=off target="_blank" href="<%= @record.domain %>/confirmation/withdrawal?tid=<%= @record.tid %>&confirmation_code=<%= @record.code %>&action=cancel">click here</a> to cancel.
      <br>
      <br>
      <br>

      ZSmart Team
      <br>
      This is an automated message, please do not reply.
    </p>
  </div>
  <p class="footer">
    Â© 2021 Zsmart.tech All Rights Reserved.
  </p>
</div>
